_______________________________________________________________________________
"Graft Weapon"     
        Through a combination of meditation on the arts of war and
        psychometabolic enhancements, a psionicist is able to act
        as if a weapon were a part of his body.  This ability, Graft
        Weapon, will increase the combat effectiveness of a single
        weapon for a moderate length of time.  The weapon must be
        unwielded when the power is initiated, and will automatically
        be wielded.  The weapon will be unwielded again when the
        power ends.  If the weapon is unwielded before then, the power
        will end prematurely.
 
SP Cost:  variable            Guild Level:  4         Potential Points:  2
 
Command:  graftw <weapon>
